This drivetrain delivers lightning-fast shifts and a 060 mph time under five seconds, while the mid-engine balance and precise steering make the Boxster S one of the most rewarding cars to drive in its class. The wind deflector enhances top-down comfort, while floor mats in interior color and premium Stone Grey leather create a refined cabin atmosphere. ARCTIC SILVER METALLIC!!! EXTRA CLEAN!!! This 2010 Porsche Boxster is in great shape. It's well equipped with a Power Convertible Top, 7 Speed PDK Transmission, Heated Leather Seats, Bose Surround Sound System, Bluetooth, Automatic Headlights, 18 Cayman S Wheels and many more luxury features. The paint and body are in excellent condition. It's originally from California, then the previous owner moved to Michigan where it was garage kept and stored in the winter. The Carfax shows minor damage reported. It was scratched in a wind storm and has been properly repaired. The black leather interior is like new! The seats look great. Even the convertible top is in excellent condition. The 18 Cayman S wheels look great and the Continental tires have plenty of tread remaining. Everything is in proper working order and all services are up to date. The top works great and the AC blows ice cold. Boxster's are fun cars and this one is in really good condition. OPTIONS: 7 speed Doppelkupplung (PDK) transmission Arctic Silver Metallic 18 Cayman S wheels Bose Surround Sound System Bluetooth interface Universal audio interface Heated Seats Automatic climate control Exterior color roll bar Original MSRP $58,455 Jon 248-549-3636 Please call first to check availability and to make an appointment for a test drive.
